<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Nueva Compra - Notificación Administrador</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #dc3545;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #dc3545;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .alert {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            color: #721c24;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .order-info {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .order-info h2 {
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .customer-info {
            background-color: #d1ecf1;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .items-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .items-table th,
        .items-table td {
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .items-table th {
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: white;
        }
        .items-table tr:nth-child(even) {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }
        .total-section {
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .total-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .total-final {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #dc3545;
            border-top: 2px solid #dc3545;
            padding-top: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .shipping-info {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .payment-info {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .status {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .status.success {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
        }
        .status.pending {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            color: #856404;
        }
        .actions {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 5px;
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: #6c757d;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🚨 Nueva Compra Recibida</h1>
            <p>Se ha realizado una nueva compra en la tienda</p>
        </div>

        <div class="alert">
            <strong>⚠️ Acción Requerida:</strong> Revisa los detalles del pedido y procede con el procesamiento.
        </div>

        <div class="order-info">
            <h2>Información del Pedido</h2>
            <p><strong>Número de Pedido:</strong> #{{orderNumber}}</p>
            <p><strong>Fecha y Hora:</strong> {{orderDate}}</p>
            <p><strong>Estado del Pago:</strong> 
                <span class="status {{#if (eq paymentStatus 'succeeded')}}success{{else}}pending{{/if}}">
                    {{#if (eq paymentStatus 'succeeded')}}Pagado{{else}}Pendiente{{/if}}
                </span>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="customer-info">
            <h3>Información del Cliente</h3>
            <p><strong>Nombre:</strong> {{userName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{userEmail}}</p>
        </div>

        <h3>Productos Comprados</h3>
        <table class="items-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Producto</th>
                    <th>Cantidad</th>
                    <th>Precio Unitario</th>
                    <th>Total</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {{#each items}}
                <tr>
                    <td>{{this.product.name}}</td>
                    <td>{{this.quantity}}</td>
                    <td>${{this.price}}</td>
                    <td>${{multiply this.quantity this.price}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{/each}}
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <div class="total-section">
            <div class="total-row">
                <span>Subtotal:</span>
                <span>${{subtotal}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="total-row">
                <span>Envío:</span>
                <span>${{shippingCost}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="total-row">
                <span>Impuestos:</span>
                <span>${{tax}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="total-row total-final">
                <span>Total:</span>
                <span>${{total}}</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="shipping-info">
            <h3>Dirección de Envío</h3>
            <p><strong>{{shippingAddress.street}}</strong></p>
            <p>{{shippingAddress.city}}, {{shippingAddress.state}} {{shippingAddress.zipCode}}</p>
            <p>{{shippingAddress.country}}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="payment-info">
            <h3>Información de Pago</h3>
            <p><strong>Método:</strong> {{paymentMethod}}</p>
            <p><strong>Estado:</strong> 
                <span class="status {{#if (eq paymentStatus 'succeeded')}}success{{else}}pending{{/if}}">
                    {{#if (eq paymentStatus 'succeeded')}}Confirmado{{else}}Pendiente{{/if}}
                </span>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="actions">
            <h3>Acciones Disponibles</h3>
            <a href="{{baseUrl}}/admin/orders/{{orderNumber}}" class="btn">Ver Pedido Completo</a>
            <a href="{{baseUrl}}/admin/orders" class="btn btn-secondary">Ver Todos los Pedidos</a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Sistema de Notificaciones - Tienda Online</strong></p>
            <p>Este es un email automático del sistema de administración.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
